data.description: Practically BRAND new home on a spacious home site in Auburndale gated community, with luxurious finishes and move-in ready features throughout! This immaculate home features four bedrooms, an open gathering room and kitchen with Quartz countertops and a versatile dining room. Relax in the luxurious owner's suite complete with, walk-in wardrobe, and spa-like en-suite with 36" raised vanities, tiled shower, and water closet. This home features…large pantry, staggered cabinets with crown moulding and decorative knobs/pulls, soft close drawers, Samsung stainless steel quiet-operation dishwasher, over-the-range microwave, smooth-top range, and Bespoke refrigerator and more. You'll find 18” x 18” ceramic tile in wet areas, upgraded wood laminate flooring in the living room, dining room and Kitchen; bedrooms all boast Mohawk stain-resistant carpet. There are ceiling fans in the gathering room and all bedrooms, upgraded 5-1/4” baseboards throughout. Save on utilities with energy efficient R-30 ceiling insulation, double-pane Low-E windows, and a programmable thermostat. You will fall in love with the 3 car garage, the vertical hardy look siding, screened lanai, and luscious grass. Come visit this beautiful house and make it your new home today!
